  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t这一下子反共浓度暴涨了，比之前的Battlefield 1俄国内战还要刺激了！（布尔什维克病毒就出自俄国内战Red Tide开场白）<br/>\n<br/>\r\n装甲列车又来了，刺激刺激！<br/>\n<br/>\r\n我下载了个<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdG9yZS5zdGVhbXBvd2VyZWQuY29tL2FwcC8xNDY5NjEwL0xhc3RfVHJhaW5fSG9tZS8\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/1469610/Last_Train_Home/\">试玩版（Steam）</a>，觉得还蛮好的<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\r\n（容易和波兰国旗混淆。捷克军团的军旗）<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYjE1MGY4ZDExZjI1ZGMxMjFkYzFkLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xOTIwJmhlaWdodD0xMDgw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b150f8d11f25dc121dc1d.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b150f8d11f25dc121dc1d.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b150f8d11f25dc121dc1d.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvOTk0Yjk1NzE0NGFmMGM1Y2UwYzBkLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xOTIwJmhlaWdodD0xMDgw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/994b957144af0c5ce0c0d.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/994b957144af0c5ce0c0d.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/994b957144af0c5ce0c0d.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNTg2ZmZmMDAzNmEyOWZlMmY0YTljLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xOTIwJmhlaWdodD0xMDgw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/586fff0036a29fe2f4a9c.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/586fff0036a29fe2f4a9c.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/586fff0036a29fe2f4a9c.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNjFkNDRjMjU5NzRhMjYwZGU4YTIwLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xOTIwJmhlaWdodD0xMDgw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/61d44c25974a260de8a20.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/61d44c25974a260de8a20.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/61d44c25974a260de8a20.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n后来这家装甲车厂赤化严重，变成了红色普蒂洛夫列宁格勒工厂，以纪念“伟大的十月革命”，再后来改名基若夫工厂，在“伟大的卫国战争”期间生产Kliment Voroshilov，KV-1型坦克<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNzJiZDNjZWYwZTA1NjBjMDA2ZmZlLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xOTIwJmhlaWdodD0xMDgw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/72bd3cef0e0560c006ffe.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/72bd3cef0e0560c006ffe.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/72bd3cef0e0560c006ffe.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvODU0OWQ5NWU5NzdhYzNjNzE0ZjdlLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xOTIwJmhlaWdodD0xMDgw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/8549d95e977ac3c714f7e.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/8549d95e977ac3c714f7e.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/8549d95e977ac3c714f7e.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvODkwNGRhMjRhOTcyMzYxNWYwODg4LmpwZz93aWR0aD0xOTIwJmhlaWdodD0xMDgw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/8904da24a9723615f0888.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/8904da24a9723615f0888.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/8904da24a9723615f0888.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n我觉得这是全世界历史上最失败的军事援助，现在全世界大部分现存的英国Mark V落入了苏联红军手里后散落在前苏联各地，以至于俄国内战后期，红军手里的Mark V比白军手里还多不少。红军用这些坦克还用到了后来“伟大的卫国战争”期间。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n我觉得现在的乌克兰捐助坦克，宁可全部被炸毁也不能被缴获<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNTgwZjAwMzUxYmMxMWFjNTI5YTg0LmpwZz93aWR0aD0xOTIwJmhlaWdodD0xMDgw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/580f00351bc11ac529a84.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/580f00351bc11ac529a84.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/580f00351bc11ac529a84.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n张作霖快乐车<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMWYyZTVjYWQ1YjhmN2MwZTQxYmJjLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xOTIwJmhlaWdodD0xMDgw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1f2e5cad5b8f7c0e41bbc.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1f2e5cad5b8f7c0e41bbc.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1f2e5cad5b8f7c0e41bbc.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n开车的方向盘姿势极为不舒适\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
